originalText.text: DO NOT MAKE THE SAME MISTAKE I DID -- DO NOT RENT WITH GARNER REALTY! I lived  at 308 West 77th Street and it was nothing but excuse after excuse from the building manager Steve. Multiple roof leaks, construction in the building that carried on for months, and a complete disregard for our privacy. On top of all of that, good luck trying to get your security deposit back and fighting their false claims. Save yourself the headache and rent with ANYBODY else! Garner is a thief!
